summary: This mod adds the Headman\'s Armor to the game and makes it strong like the daedra armor
descriptionHtml:
You would like to look like a headman? No problem. This mod adds the headman\'s armor an Weapon to the game. The also strong like the daedra armor. Please look at the read me, before you install the mod. This items are not craftable an must be add with the commandwindow.

Known bugs:

In the first-person the gloves look buggy.
author: Aredian
